# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]

### Added
- VPN Browser Extension (Chrome, Edge, Firefox)
- CRX build script for creating browser extensions
- GitHub Actions workflow for automated releases
- Version bump workflow
- CRX build workflow for CI/CD

### Changed
- Updated all documentation to reflect VPN extension
- Enhanced README files with extension installation guides
- Improved project structure documentation

### Fixed
- N/A

## [1.0.0] - 2025-06-10

### Added
- Initial release of MOVTIGROUP VPN extension
- Core visual design components
- Responsive layout system
- VPN Browser Extension
  - Chrome support (CRX)
  - Edge support (CRX)
  - Firefox support (ZIP)
- GitHub Actions workflows:
  - Automated release with CRX building
  - Version bump automation
  - CI/CD for CRX builds
- Bilingual support (Persian/Farsi and English)
- Comprehensive documentation
- MIT License

### Changed
- Updated README.md, README.fa.md, README.en.md, README.zh.md
- Enhanced AGENTS.md with detailed AI assistant guidelines
- Improved CHANGELOG with version history

### Fixed
- N/A

